body:
This PR introduces support for benchmarking against the `zdwiel` dataset and makes dataset selection configurable instead of fixed to `dataset01`.

It adds a `--dataset` option to the benchmark shell script and CLI, loads datasets dynamically, applies dataset-specific scenario filtering, includes dataset information in benchmark output, and adds a dedicated `zdwiel` fixture for browsing/debugging benchmark circuits. It also adds the `zdwiel-dataset` dependency required for the new workflow.


